# 1. Python Application Monitoring

Install Datadog libraries:

```bash
pip install ddtrace datadog
```

### Flask Application Instrumentation

```python
from flask import Flask
from ddtrace import patch_all

patch_all()

app = Flask(__name__)

@app.route("/users")
def users():
    return {"status": "success"}

if __name__ == "__main__":
    app.run()
```

### Custom Metrics

```python
from datadog import initialize, statsd

options = {
    "api_key": "YOUR_API_KEY",
    "app_key": "YOUR_APP_KEY"
}

initialize(**options)

statsd.increment(
    "user.login.success"
)

statsd.gauge(
    "active.users",
    125
)
```

Metrics visible in Datadog:

```text
user.login.success
active.users
```

