# 1. Datadog Fundamentals

## Agent Installation (Linux)

```bash
DD_API_KEY=<YOUR_API_KEY> \
bash -c "$(curl -L https://s3.amazonaws.com/dd-agent/scripts/install_script.sh)"
```

Verify:

```bash
sudo datadog-agent status
```

Agent collects:

* CPU
* Memory
* Disk
* Network
* Application metrics
* Logs

