## C++

Datadog doesn't provide full native APM like Java/Python.

Use OpenTelemetry:

```cpp
auto tracer =
opentelemetry::trace::Provider::GetTracerProvider()
->GetTracer("cpp-service");
```

Send traces to Datadog via OTEL Collector.

