## Custom CloudWatch Metric (Python)

```python
import boto3

cloudwatch = boto3.client('cloudwatch')

cloudwatch.put_metric_data(
 Namespace='CustomApp',
 MetricData=[
 {
  'MetricName':'Orders',
  'Value':500
 }
 ]
)
```

